column2: Shanna, the She-Devil: Survival of the Fittest (2007) #2
column6:
The jungle action continues as Shanna the She-Devil squares off against gangsters, raptors and Neanderthal Nazi apes! But will Shanna be able to protect her new guests on the island-including Dirk and his pirate crew-or will the swashbucklers be raptor food?,2007,9
32 PGS./Parental Advisory ...$2.99
column8: | penciller (cover):Khari Evans | writer:Justin Gray | letterer:Dave Lanphear | inker:Jimmy Palmiotti | colorist:Christina Strain
